  ('54e80fdb-1f52-55db-b4f4-77bf29f98fb4', '6ff1a99c-0aad-5f5d-80bf-603c9b4d05bc', 'A(−1 ; 2) وB(3 ; 2). ما إحداثيّات الشعاع AB؟', '[{"id":"a","text":"(2 ; 4)"},{"id":"b","text":"(−4 ; 0)"},{"id":"c","text":"(2 ; 0)"},{"id":"d","text":"(4 ; 0)"}]'::jsonb, 'd', 'AB = (xB − xA ; yB − yA) = (3 − (−1) ; 2 − 2) = (4 ; 0).', 3)
